              barns of the farmstead, and secretly acts as their guardian. If
              treated well, they protect the family and animals from evil and
              misfortune, and may also aid the chores and farm work. We felt
              this creature fit the brand well, as our product would ‘look after
              the house’ - so we came up with ‘tontu’ as the company name.
