        the energy they are using. For this reason
        <strong class="font-medium">infographics</strong> were relied upon
        heavily, as well as only showing
        <strong class="font-medium">crucial information</strong> on the app.
        Furthermore, <strong class="font-medium">large numbers</strong> were
        used for <strong class="font-medium">key statistics</strong> on pages to
        stand out. The app screens were designed in
        <strong class="font-medium">Adobe Xd</strong> so that a
        <strong class="font-medium">mock functional prototype</strong> could be
